### Get all courses
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/courses/

###

### Create a course
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/courses/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Database Management Systems",
    "code": "CS101",
    "credits": 4
}

###

### Create another course
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/courses/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Operating Systems",
    "code": "CS102",
    "credits": 3
}

###

### Get course by ID
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/courses/1

###

### Update a course
PUT http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/courses/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Advanced DBMS",
    "code": "CS101",
    "credits": 5
}

###

### Delete a course
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/courses/2

###

### Verify remaining courses
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/courses/